Class HttpUpload

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable

    public class HttpUpload
extends HttpTransfer
    Connects via HTTP to a URL and uploads the specified file. Examples: 
      <httpupload file="./index.html" url="http://www.centurylink.com/index.html"/>
    Uploads index.html from the current directory to centurylink.com.
